width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/eCkQEWMXk2uzWSVk8cpktYuuD9n.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/kqCMMLnoWO46xvPyPcDW9CZFJ4d.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/cJnNRpN2NTgDTE1YcwvglEYoq5v.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/639rLU9bip7blw5QKyoFaV1M7eE.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/tGaASzUEqDr2pucM6ZBgZkooztf.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/ihDqZdTn8voHPXSCLZjUa6IHzMt.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/1L4yYvtSPWtglsiwL7W7hCIpbIl.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-25T14:19:55.974+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Dangal","runtime":161,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Dangal is an extraordinary true story based on the life of Mahavir Singh and his two daughters, Geeta and Babita Phogat. The film traces the inspirational journey of a father who trains his daughters to become world class wrestlers."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Dangal","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Mahavir Singh Phogat (Aamir Khan) býval vynikající zápasník, ale musel nechat sportu, aby si našel práci, která ho uživí. Doufá, že jednou aspoň jeho syn vyhraje pro Indii medaili. Jenomže se mu narodí samé dcery, a tak zklamaný Mahavir na svůj sen pomalu zapomíná. Pak si ale přijdou rodiče dvou chlapců stěžovat, že Mahavirovy dcery zbily jejich syny. Dívky se k tomu přiznají a Mahavir si uvědomí, že i když má dcery, ještě to neznamená, že z nich nemůže vychovat zápasníky. K překvapení a nelibosti celé vesnice je začne trénovat k zápasení."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"Dangal","runtime":161,"tagline":"Kızlarım erkeklerden daha aşağı değiller","homepage":"","overview":"2010 Olimpiyat Oyunları… Hindistan, tarihi boyunca güreş dalında hiç altın madalya kazanmamıştı. O yıl yarışa 22 yaşındaki Geeta Phogat katıldı. Olimpiyatlara Hindistan'ı temsilen katılan ilk kadın güreşçi olan Geeta, aslında hiç \"profesyonel\" güreş eğitimi almamıştı. Onu, genç yaştan itibaren kendisi de güreşçi olan babası yetiştirmişti. Ama Geeta, tüm engelleri aşarak Hindistan'a güreş dalında altın madalya getiren ilk sporcusu olmayı başararak tarihe geçti. 2014 yılında yapılan bir sonraki Olimpiyat oyunlarında ise Geeta'nın kız kardeşi Babita Kumari, ülkeye bir altın madalya daha kazandırdı."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"摔跤吧！爸爸","runtime":140,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"　　马哈维亚·辛格·珀尕（阿米尔·汗 Aamir Khan 饰）曾是印度国家摔跤冠军，因生活所迫放弃摔跤。他希望让儿子可以帮他完成梦想——赢得世界级金牌。结果生了四个女儿本以为梦想就此破碎的辛格却意外发现女儿身上的惊人天赋，看到冠军希望的他决定不能让女儿的天赋浪费，像其他女孩一样只能洗衣做饭过一生 ，再三考虑之后，与妻子约定一年时间按照摔跤手的标准训练两个女儿：换掉裙子 、剪掉了长发，让她们练习摔跤，并赢得一个又一个冠军，最终赢来了成为榜样激励千千万万女性的机会……"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"מתאבקות לחלום","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"סיפורם האמיתי ויוצא דופן של מהביר סינג פוגט, ושתי בנותיו, גיטה ובביטה מכפר קטן בהודו. הסרט עוקב אחר המסע מעורר ההשראה שלהם לזכות במדליית זהב ראשונה להודו בענף ההיאבקות. מהביר, מתאבק לשעבר, מאמן את בנותיו להיות מתאבקות ברמה עולמית, יחד עם הקושי להתגבר על דעות קדומות ולפרוץ בספורט שנשלט על-ידי גברים."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"我和我的冠軍女兒","runtime":161,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"「摔跤是男生的事」  「為何你覺得我們家的女孩會輸呢？」  改編自印度摔跤選手瑪哈維亞的傳奇感人故事，由印度天王阿米爾罕主演。瑪哈維亞是摔跤金牌得主，卻因生活與體制問題而放棄摔跤夢。他一心一意能生個兒子，一圓當年未盡夢想，卻命運弄人，連生四女。一個偶然，他發現兩個女兒的摔跤天分，開始訓練她們摔跤，過程酸甜苦辣，這幫父女怎麼面對來自四面八方的輿論、歧視？他們又真的獲得最後的勝利嗎？"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Dangal","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Mahavir Singh Phogat es un entrenador de lucha libre que prepara a sus hijas Babita Kumari y Geeta."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Dangal","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Były zapaśnik Mahavir Singh Phogat naucza zapasów swoje dwie córki, walcząc tym samym ze stereotypami."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Дангал","runtime":160,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Когда-то Махавир Сингх Пхогат был чемпионом Индии по борьбе. По причине бедности он был вынужден бросить спорт, но поклялся воспитать сына, который станет в будущем олимпийским чемпионом. Но вот досада — у них с женой родились четыре дочки. Отец сначала отчаялся, но потом, увидев, что подросшие девчонки поколачивают одноклассников, решил всё же сделать из них спортсменок."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"당갈","runtime":0,"tagline":"“남자든 여자든 금메달은 금메달인데!” 누구도 예상하지 못한 뒤집기 한판승!","homepage":"","overview":"전직 레슬링 선수였던 ‘마하비르 싱 포갓(아미르 칸)’은 아버지의 반대로 금메달의 꿈을 이루지 못한 채 레슬링을 포기한다. 아들을 통해 꿈을 이루겠다는 생각은 내리 딸만 넷이 태어나면서 좌절된다. 그러던 어느 날, 두 딸이 또래 남자아이들을 신나게 때린 모습에서 잠재력을 발견하고 레슬링 특훈에 돌입한다. 사람들의 따가운 시선과 조롱에도 불구하고 첫째 기타(파티마 사나이 샤크)와 둘째 바비타(삼아 말호 트라)는 아버지의 훈련 속에 재능을 발휘, 승승장구 승리를 거두며 국가대표 레슬러로까지 성장해 마침내 국제대회에 출전한다.하지만 세계의 벽은 높기만 하고 끝없이 이어지는 슬럼프로 연이은 패배만 이어지는데…\r 인도를 넘어 전 세계적으로 흥행 기록을 이어가고 있는 당갈은 레슬링을 가리키는 힌디어다. 딸을 레슬링 선수로 키워낸 한 남자의 실화를 바탕으로 아미르 칸이 제작에 참여했으며, 엄격하지만 부성이 넘치는 아빠로 출연해 흥행 신화를 기록한 올해 최고의 화제작."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Dangal","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Dangal - Die Hoffnung auf den großen Sieg","runtime":161,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Mahavir ist leidenschaftlicher Ringer, und auf dem Weg nach ganz oben. Sein Vater zwingt ihn jedoch, den Kampfsport aufzugeben. Also will Mahavir später seinem eigenen Sohn ermöglichen, Ringer zu werden, wenn dieser denn will. Dann bekommt er vier Töchter, und sein ersehntes Ziel scheint in weite Ferne zu rücken - bis sich das Blatt wendet. Wer hätte gedacht, dass auch die Töchter plötzlich Talent fürs Wrestling an den Tag legen?"},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Dangal","runtime":161,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Un ancien champion de lutte cherche à décrocher la médaille d'or qu'il n'a jamais remportée en entraînant deux de ses filles pour les Jeux du Commonwealth."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"مسابقة المصارعة","runtime":161,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"تدور احداث الفيلم حول ماهافير سينجا بوهجات بطل سابق في لعبة المصارعة، يحلم بالفوز بميدالية ذهبية لصالح بلاده، ويتعهد بأن يجعل ابنه المستقبلي يحقق ما لم يستطيع تحقيقه، لكنه ينجب أربع فتيات، ويظن أن الحلم ميئوس منه، حتى يكتشف موهبة اثنتان منهما بعد ضربهما لولدين، ويقرر تدريبهما على أصول اللعبة."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"Dangal","runtime":161,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Mahavir moet zijn droom opgeven door financiële moeilijkheden. Hij besluit dat als hij geen gouden medaille kan winnen dat zijn zoon het op een dag zal moeten doen. Over een periode van 20 jaar krijgen hij en zijn vrouw vier kinderen, allemaal meisjes."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Dangal","runtime":160,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"A Dangal című életrajzi film Mahavir Singh Phogat életét mutatja be, aki birkózásra tanította lányait, Babita Kumarit és Geeta Phogatot. Ennek köszönhetően Geeta Phogat lett az első indiai birkózónő, aki aranyérmet szerzett a 2010-es Nemzetközösségi játékokon 52 kg, míg testvére, Babita Kumari ezüstérmes lett az 55 kilogrammos mezőnyben."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Борба","runtime":161,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Махавир Сингх (Амир Хан) е бивш национален шампион по борба на Индия, който не успява да сбъдне мечтата си да стане световен шампион и затова се зарича, когато му се роди син, да го тренира и той да я осъществи. Но как ще стане това, след като му се раждат 4 дъщери...Филмът е базиран на действителни събития."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"Dangal","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"En engang lovende bryder jagter den guldmedalje, han aldrig vandt, ved at træne to af sine døtre til Commonwealth Games."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"Данґал","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Історія реально існуючого спортсмена Махавіра Сінгха Пхогата, який через бідність був змушений кинути спортивну боротьбу, але поклявся виховати сина, який стане в майбутньому олімпійським чемпіоном. Але от прикрість - у них з дружиною народилися чотири дочки. Батько спочатку був у відчаї, але потім, побачивши, що дівчата б'ють однокласників, вирішив все ж зробити з них спортсменок. Тренер з батька вийшов відмінний."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"Dangalas","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Pasakojimas apie sportininką Mahavirą Singhą Phogatą, kuris dėl skurdo buvo priverstas pasitraukti iš sporto, tačiau pažadėjo kai gims sūnus, kuris ateityje taps olimpiniu čempionu. Bet likimas lėmė - jie turėjo su žmoma keturias dukteris. Tėvas buvo praradęs viltį, bet kai jo merginas supykdė klasiokai, ir jos sumušė juos. Tėvui atsirado viltis.Geeta Phogat buvo pirmoji Indijos čempionė, laimėjusi 2010 m. Tarptautines žaidynes, kur laimėjo aukso medalį, o jos sesuo Babita Kumari laimėjo sidabrą."},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"},{"data":{"title":"ปล้ำฝันสนั่นโลก","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"สร้างจากเรื่องจริงของนักมวยปล้ำหญิง เรื่องราวของมหาวีร์ (อาเมียร์ ข่าน) เป็นอดีตนักมวยปล้ำที่ต้องทิ้งความฝัน ที่จะชนะเหรียญทองการแข่งขันระดับโลกให้แก่ประเทศอินเดียไป เนื่องจากว่าขาดเงินช่วยเหลือเงินสนับสนุนเพียงพอ แต่ว่ามหาวีร์ยังไม่ยินยอมทิ้งความฝันนั้นไปซะทีเดียว เนื่องจากว่าเขาตั้งอกตั้งใจว่าจะฝึกหัดลูกชายของเขาในอนาคตให้ดำเนินรอยตามทางมวยปล้ำเส้นเดียวกับที่เขาเคยเดินให้ได้ ถ้าว่าชะตากรรมกลับตีเส้นทางให้เขาอีกแบบหนึ่งตลอด 2 ทศวรรษก่อนหน้าที่ผ่านมา มหาวีร์กลับไม่มีลูกชายเลย มีก็เพียงแต่บุตรสาวอีกทั้ง 4 คน อยู่มาวันหนึ่งบุตรสาวคนโต 2 คน กลับไปวิวาทกับกรุ๊ปเด็กชายถึงกับขนาดลงไม้ลงมือ ทำให้มหาวีร์ใส่ใจได้ว่าบุตรสาวของเขานั่นแหละที่ได้พรวสรรค์จากเขาไป ความมุ่งมาดของเขาก็เลยกลับมาเจิดจ้าอีกรอบ มหาวีร์ก็เลยตั้งความมุ่งหมายไว้ว่าจะแปลงบุตรสาวให้แปลงเป็นนักมวยปลุกปล้ำสุดยอด ให้พสกคุณฝึกซ้อมไปกับเด็กชายในหมู่บ้าน ส่งเสริมให้พวกคุณต่อสู้ หมายมั่นความมีชัย ไม่ว่าจะมีปัญหาแค่ไหนมากีดขวางก็ตาม"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"打死不離 3 父女","runtime":161,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"前摔跤運動員瑪哈維，一直希望培育下一代成為金牌選手，為國爭光，可惜聯生四位千金令他幾乎拋棄夢想。偶然他發現兩個女吉塔和芭碧塔竟擁有摔跤天份，打架比男生還要兇狠。於是決定要訓練她們成為 No. 1 摔跤選手！過程中，3 父女要打低的不只是比賽對手，還有男尊女卑的社會觀念、各種攻擊性的輿論及歧視. . . . . . 他們最終能否戰勝一切，攜手邁向奪金之路？"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Dangal","runtime":161,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Un fost campion de lupte se opune corupției și opresiunii societății și își crește cele două fiice să devină campioane la sportul la care și el a excelat."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Dangal","runtime":161,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Um ex-lutador treina duas de suas filhas para competirem nos Jogos da Commonwealth e ganharem a medalha de ouro que ele nunca conquistou."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Dangal","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"داستان فیلم که بر اساس واقعیت ساخته شده درباره یک کشتی‌گیر هندی به نام ماهاویر سینگ است که قصد دارد به دخترانش کشتی یاد دهد تا در مسابقات جهانی مدال طلا کسب کنند اما... ..."},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"Dangal","runtime":161,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ο Mahavir είναι πρώην παλαιστής. Αναγκάστηκε να εγκαταλείψει το άθλημα προκειμένου να αποκτήσει αμειβόμενη απασχόληση, όμως αποφασίζει να εκπαιδεύσει τους μελλοντικούς γιους του, ώστε να ακολουθήσουν την πορεία του. Με στόχο ένα χρυσό μετάλλιο σε διεθνές επίπεδο, στην πάλη ανδρών, με τη γυναίκα του κάνουν τέσσερις κόρες!!! Πλέον το όνειρό του φαίνεται να αργοπεθαίνει, ωστόσο τα κορίτσια μπορούν να παλέψουν, ακριβώς όπως οι άντρες."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"Huấn Luyện Viên Đấu Vật","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Dangal là bộ phim thể thao (đấu vật) tiểu sử kể về quá trình võ sĩ Mahavir Singh Phogat dạy đấu vật cho 2 cô con gái, thể hiện sức mạnh của phái nữ, dẫn dắt 2 cô đến với thành công. Bộ phim đề cao sức mạnh của người phụ nữ, khuyến khích phụ nữ tham gia thể thao và đề cao tinh thần tự hào dân tộc"},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Dangal","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Dangal es una historia verdadera extraordinaria basada en la vida de Mahavir Singh y sus dos hijas, Geeta y Babita Phogat. La película traza el viaje inspirador de un padre que entrena a sus hijas para convertirse en luchadores de clase mundial."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"ダンガル きっと、つよくなる","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"დანგალი","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"სპორტსმენის მაჰავირ სინგ ფოგატის ისტორია, რომელიც სიღარიბის გამო იძულებული გახდა დაეტოვებინა ჭიდაობა, მაგრამ პირობა დადო, რომ გაზრდიდა თავის შვილს, რომელიც მომავალში ოლიმპიური ჩემპიონი გახდებოდა. მაგრამ აქ არის გაღიზიანება - მას და მის მეუღლეს ოთხი ქალიშვილი შეეძინათ. მამა თავიდან სასოწარკვეთილებაში ჩავარდა, მაგრამ შემდეგ, როცა ხედავდა, რომ მოზრდილი გოგოები სცემდნენ თანაკლასელებს, გადაწყვიტა მათგან სპორტსმენები გაეკეთებინა. მამაჩემის მწვრთნელი შესანიშნავი გამოდგა."},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"Dangal","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Uma ex-promessa da luta livre persegue a medalha de ouro que nunca ganhou ao treinar duas das suas filhas para competir nos Jogos da Commonwealth."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"5a0b29c492514130ed01d7a2","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/5a0b29c492514130ed01d7a2","author":"Svumpukkel85","content":"$11","created_at":"2017-11-14T17:37:08.495Z","updated_at":"2021-06-23T15:58:02.740Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":null,"username":"Svumpukkel85","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"5fb689c3f29d66003b338edd","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/5fb689c3f29d66003b338edd","author":"r96sk","content":"$12","created_at":"2020-11-19T15:05:39.208Z","updated_at":"2021-06-23T15:58:47.743Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":6,"username":"r96sk","avatar_path":"/mwR7rFHoDcobAx1i61I3skzMW3U.jpg"}}],"recommendations":[{"id":441889,"adult":false,"title":"Secret Superstar","video":false,"overview":"A talented teenage singer-songwriter living amid domestic abuse becomes a YouTube sensation after a video in which she hides her identity goes viral.","genre_ids":[18,10402],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6861,"vote_count":188,"poster_path":"/fkTeziNtc0uwE899uI1hlMOEdZL.jpg","release_date":"2017-10-19","vote_average":7.261,"backdrop_path":"/yrQTyiJpki9dCuIU0bGhGXBu7Zh.jpg","original_title":"सीक्रेट सुपरस्टार","original_language":"hi"},{"id":297222,"adult":false,"title":"PK","video":false,"overview":"A stranger in the city asks questions no one has asked before. Known only by his initials, the man's innocent questions and childlike curiosity take him on a journey of love, laughter and letting go.","genre_ids":[35,18,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.6684,"vote_count":1118,"poster_path":"/z2x2Y4tncefsIU7h82gmUM5vnBJ.jpg","release_date":"2014-12-18","vote_average":7.707,"backdrop_path":"/gxfvtq5eYiClS2X7hxAAPBNrbWA.jpg","original_title":"पीके","original_language":"hi"},{"id":19666,"adult":false,"title":"Lagaan: Once Upon a Time in India","video":false,"overview":"The year is 1893 and India is under British occupation. In a small village, the tyrannical Captain Russell has imposed an unprecedented land tax on its citizens. Outraged, Bhuvan, a rebellious farmer, rallies the villagers to publicly oppose the tax. Russell offers a novel way to settle the dispute: he challenges Bhuvan and his men to a game of cricket, a sport completely foreign to India. If Bhuvan and his men can defeat Russell's team, the tax will be repealed.","genre_ids":[12,18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.6318,"vote_count":620,"poster_path":"/yNX9lFRAFeNLNRIXdqZK9gYrYKa.jpg","release_date":"2001-06-15","vote_average":7.262,"backdrop_path":"/76VwduxQMkVXOUktps85dE0lLeP.jpg","original_title":"लगान","original_language":"hi"},{"id":7508,"adult":false,"title":"Like Stars on Earth","video":false,"overview":"Ishaan Awasthi is an eight-year-old whose world is filled with wonders that no one else seems to appreciate. Colours, fish, dogs, and kites don't seem important to the adults, who are much more interested in things like homework, marks, and neatness. Ishaan cannot seem to get anything right in class; he is then sent to boarding school, where his life changes forever.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.3589,"vote_count":1291,"poster_path":"/puHRt6Raovm5ujGCdwLWvRv4NHU.jpg","release_date":"2007-12-21","vote_average":7.952,"backdrop_path":"/bPwdy3zaNnMdZ22u0WCcYu0xxgt.jpg","original_title":"तारे ज़मीन पर","original_language":"hi"},{"id":376812,"adult":false,"title":"Sultan","video":false,"overview":"The ageing wrestler Sultan Ali Khan decides to try his luck on the mat again; to do this, he wants to represent his country at the Olympic Games, but first has to overcome personal issues.","genre_ids":[18,28,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.1977,"vote_count":251,"poster_path":"/vPTYtKuV8X5uUd3SqnzO14W6Dti.jpg","release_date":"2016-07-06","vote_average":6.898,"backdrop_path":"/74bUfGDD0kJ53M334vQcbJRzsI8.jpg","original_title":"सुल्तान","original_language":"hi"},{"id":20453,"adult":false,"title":"3 Idiots","video":false,"overview":"Rascal. Joker. Dreamer. Genius... You've never met a college student quite like \"Rancho.\" From the moment he arrives at India's most prestigious university, Rancho's outlandish schemes turn the campus upside down—along with the lives of his two newfound best friends. Together, they make life miserable for \"Virus,\" the school’s uptight and heartless dean. But when Rancho catches the eye of the dean's daughter, Virus sets his sights on flunking out the \"3 idiots\" once and for all.","genre_ids":[18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.5657,"vote_count":2642,"poster_path":"/66A9MqXOyVFCssoloscw79z8Tew.jpg","release_date":"2009-12-23","vote_average":7.997,"backdrop_path":"/8gT3UKtglLVpu0YfccwbmXZ5Eis.jpg","original_title":"3 Idiots","original_language":"hi"},{"id":388333,"adult":false,"title":"M.S. Dhoni: The Untold Story","video":false,"overview":"Based on the life story of Mahendra Singh Dhoni, and his journey to being the world cup winning captain of the Indian cricket team.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6858,"vote_count":194,"poster_path":"/lUpMckVHaB55YJ3SMK0arwxKmCt.jpg","release_date":"2016-09-30","vote_average":7.2,"backdrop_path":"/oQCrHuAqqQCJ5H2gvAbsXd0T4Sw.jpg","original_title":"M.S. Dhoni: The Untold Story","original_language":"hi"},{"id":44977,"adult":false,"title":"Dhoom 3","video":false,"overview":"To avenge his father's death, a circus entertainer trained in magic and acrobatics robs banks to take down a corrupt bank owner. Two cops from Mumbai are assigned to the case.","genre_ids":[28,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.4929,"vote_count":302,"poster_path":"/rUVTM5EQUQ2I0fcfE46AkvBYWae.jpg","release_date":"2013-12-19","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/m715Fj5VVCXfwzqbCZFhmJBH8S9.jpg","original_title":"धूम ३","original_language":"hi"},{"id":370665,"adult":false,"title":"Dilwale","video":false,"overview":"Raj is a Mafia member. One day he meet a girl (Meera) while chasing by his rival gang and falls in love with her. Later he finds out that this girl is the daughter of the leader of his rival gang. Yet their love story continues until he was shot by his girlfriend upon a deep misunderstanding. After that incident these two lovers lives separate until their siblings fallen in love. With this new love story their paths intertwines again.","genre_ids":[80,28,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.7062,"vote_count":335,"poster_path":"/pYgPu6hhOr61knwbestTx4vSdMb.jpg","release_date":"2015-12-18","vote_average":6.618,"backdrop_path":"/6wnvu7YAHncMhwKs9YDrhKd98zO.jpg","original_title":"दिलवाले","original_language":"hi"},{"id":14163,"adult":false,"title":"Chak De! India","video":false,"overview":"A team of rag-tag girls with their own agenda form Team India competing for international fame in field hockey. Their coach, the ex-men's Indian National team captain, returns from a life of shame after being unjustly accused of match fixing in his last match. Can he give the girls the motivation required to win, while dealing with the shadows of his own past?","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8431,"vote_count":363,"poster_path":"/9wP26QtbLUADWsfZZ8v2sJDWKdZ.jpg","release_date":"2007-08-09","vote_average":7.2,"backdrop_path":"/wvmxctQLD1vHZvsP1Rhe0mZLb26.jpg","original_title":"चकदे! इंडिया","original_language":"hi"},{"id":7913,"adult":false,"title":"Rang De Basanti","video":false,"overview":"After a group of friends graduate from Delhi University, they listlessly haunt their old campus, until a British filmmaker casts them in a film she's making about freedom fighters under British rule. Although the group is largely apolitical, the tragic death of a friend owing to local government corruption awakens their patriotism. Inspired by the freedom fighters they represent in the film, the friends collectively decide to avenge the killing.","genre_ids":[35,18,36,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0505,"vote_count":486,"poster_path":"/f1bF8CHzEu621bPSIg6XiUNAabh.jpg","release_date":"2006-01-26","vote_average":7.083,"backdrop_path":"/fgRhyGbMAolDsQ65VRBRBtVQZNn.jpg","original_title":"रंग दे बसंती","original_language":"hi"},{"id":413543,"adult":false,"title":"Dear Zindagi","video":false,"overview":"An unconventional thinker helps a budding cinematographer gain a new perspective on life.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6842,"vote_count":250,"poster_path":"/oUg0N2isgZ5rrxdXnsemcKolfKZ.jpg","release_date":"2016-11-23","vote_average":7.042,"backdrop_path":"/d2plahqbICvNTAvhk2lM0HojJGG.jpg","original_title":"Dear Zindagi","original_language":"hi"},{"id":10757,"adult":false,"title":"Kabhi Khushi Kabhie Gham","video":false,"overview":"Years after his father disowns his adopted brother for marrying a woman of lower social standing, a young man goes on a mission to reunite his family.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.7601,"vote_count":588,"poster_path":"/12BvYKueY0eruZuTYIextEZaCC.jpg","release_date":"2001-12-14","vote_average":7.7,"backdrop_path":"/sPMBiyjTco4JdKojlfGIz5Wd0jC.jpg","original_title":"कभी ख़ुशी कभी ग़म","original_language":"hi"},{"id":393441,"adult":false,"title":"Dishoom","video":false,"overview":"When India's top cricketer is kidnapped in the Middle East, a loose cannon and a rookie cop are tasked with finding him before the high-stakes match with Pakistan.","genre_ids":[35,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6347,"vote_count":95,"poster_path":"/sY58lhquOEISrpcIzbKNV6qHgvG.jpg","release_date":"2016-07-29","vote_average":5.5,"backdrop_path":"/hrb12tCxe8N2dqFDmOJkRSa6w1g.jpg","original_title":"ढिशुम","original_language":"hi"},{"id":103243,"adult":false,"title":"Vicky Donor","video":false,"overview":"A man is brought in by an infertility doctor to supply him with his sperm, where he becomes the biggest sperm donor for his clinic.","genre_ids":[35,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4363,"vote_count":188,"poster_path":"/u8AO7DgcVYkVSXeU7oQdlhMFwcN.jpg","release_date":"2012-04-20","vote_average":6.771,"backdrop_path":"/gHDMBYpp5NZtkyFFPIRLJJUshFi.jpg","original_title":"विक्की डोनर","original_language":"hi"},{"id":537021,"adult":false,"title":"Yuli","video":false,"overview":"Yuli is the nickname given to Carlos Acosta by his father, Pedro, who considers him the son of Ogun, an African god and a fighter. As a child Yuli avoids discipline and education, learning from the streets of an impoverished and abandoned Havana. His father, however, has other ideas, and knowing that his son has a natural talent for dance, sends him to the National Ballet School of Cuba. Despite his repeated escapes and initial poor behaviour, the boy is inevitably drawn to the world of dance, and begins to shape his legendary career from a young age, becoming the first black dancer to be cast in some of the most prestigious ballet roles, originally written for white dancers, in companies such as the Houston Ballet or the Royal Ballet in London.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5359,"vote_count":97,"poster_path":"/hGGbrGNLqB0SSdH9DCuas3mSAv6.jpg","release_date":"2018-12-14","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/cBmHr3lCEbGxxNX7gQl9HiC1enL.jpg","original_title":"Yuli","original_language":"es"},{"id":917,"adult":false,"title":"Mother India","video":false,"overview":"A poverty-stricken woman raises her sons through many trials and tribulations. But no matter the struggles, always sticks to her own moral code.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5246,"vote_count":101,"poster_path":"/AlfM9yLcK1rhv73iNbDiOU9vnnu.jpg","release_date":"1957-02-13","vote_average":7.1,"backdrop_path":"/abU2NXnnwisg56vD1Lbg7Ui63GG.jpg","original_title":"मदर इण्डिया","original_language":"hi"},{"id":171158,"adult":false,"title":"Government Woman","video":false,"overview":"Xate is an ordinary woman from Midyat with eight children in tow. The only thing that sets her apart is her husband's job as Mayor of Midyat. Until, that is, an extraordinary day changes her life - and the lives of everyone else in Midyat. For the illiterate, uneducated Xate becomes Mayor of Midyat! While she takes on her mayoral duties much as she does those in her house, the infantile rivalry between her children in municipal matters leads to adventures that have the Midyat folk howling with laughter.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.4011,"vote_count":68,"poster_path":"/fOjnfISRtU9pJinlJxHX3YrPVQE.jpg","release_date":"2013-02-01","vote_average":6.037,"backdrop_path":"/zPfIEKhdjy2t8CSq256DNcWHp6W.jpg","original_title":"Hükümet Kadın","original_language":"tr"},{"id":53093,"adult":false,"title":"West and Soda","video":false,"overview":"Traditionally-animated Italian feature film directed by Bruno Bozzetto. A parody of the traditional American Western.","genre_ids":[16,37,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3046,"vote_count":65,"poster_path":"/zeSxgjtzoVfoxvM3iPe4R9SaWpK.jpg","release_date":"1965-10-01","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/S2FrfQSROcfXvPrsnOkfofDBBm.jpg","original_title":"West and Soda","original_language":"it"},{"id":504080,"adult":false,"title":"Dhadak","video":false,"overview":"Madhukar and Parthavi fall head over heels in love with each other, but the fact that they belong to different castes of society, becomes an obstacle in their romance. The lovers dare to go against societal norms and battle all odds for the sake of love.","genre_ids":[10749,18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7237,"vote_count":57,"poster_path":"/vIVKzzPA7hrSZpEwofB7Luo83kO.jpg","release_date":"2018-07-20","vote_average":6.947,"backdrop_path":"/3BrGn1hzfT4SlpooyPbpdcajFez.jpg","original_title":"धड़क","original_language":"hi"}],"similar_content":[{"id":1124876,"adult":false,"title":"Ulajh","video":false,"overview":"The journey of a young IFS officer, belonging to a prominent family of patriots, who gets embroiled in a dangerous personal conspiracy while far from her home turf, at a career-defining post.","genre_ids":[18,53],"popularity":0.4481,"vote_count":13,"poster_path":"/tRTaE89m8As6G6aqgYjCBmm6MKN.jpg","release_date":"2024-08-02","vote_average":5.462,"backdrop_path":"/gOvb0MWKeg97AWr7Cpvi3aDnB0r.jpg","original_title":"Ulajh","original_language":"hi"},{"id":162,"adult":false,"title":"Edward Scissorhands","video":false,"overview":"A small suburban town receives a visit from a castaway unfinished science experiment named Edward.","genre_ids":[14,18,10749],"popularity":9.0172,"vote_count":13586,"poster_path":"/e0FqKFvGPdQNWG8tF9cZBtev9Em.jpg","release_date":"1990-12-07","vote_average":7.719,"backdrop_path":"/uNLIMPxknsV4n3IAEDpS1iqF5dm.jpg","original_title":"Edward Scissorhands","original_language":"en"},{"id":166,"adult":false,"title":"The Party","video":false,"overview":"A thirteen-year-old French girl deals with moving to a new city and school in Paris, while at the same time her parents are getting a divorce.","genre_ids":[18,10749,35],"popularity":3.2982,"vote_count":