eat to their security when she falls in love with a boy she meets on the beach.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.2208,"vote_count":64,"poster_path":"/wQoYYvXYaeZNsGPtP1vvvyTmuhF.jpg","release_date":"2001-02-01","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/xCkTEYAF5mQIgJzdqhrqoI8IXll.jpg","original_title":"Die innere Sicherheit","original_language":"de"},{"id":194,"adult":false,"title":"Amélie","video":false,"overview":"At a tiny Parisian café, the adorable yet painfully shy Amélie accidentally discovers a gift for helping others. Soon Amelie is spending her days as a matchmaker, guardian angel, and all-around do-gooder. But when she bumps into a handsome stranger, will she find the courage to become the star of her very own love story?","genre_ids":[35,10749],"popularity":7.7969,"vote_count":12218,"poster_path":"/nSxDa3M9aMvGVLoItzWTepQ5h5d.jpg","release_date":"2001-04-25","vote_average":7.916,"backdrop_path":"/6n53UI4mX9QMfe2S0Pgt8mGebY1.jpg","original_title":"Le Fabuleux Destin d'Amélie Poulain","original_language":"fr"},{"id":247117,"adult":false,"title":"Concert at the End of Summer","video":false,"overview":"A docudrama about four weeks in the life of famous Czech composer Antonin Dvorak. The drama - filled with many of Dvorak's compositions - begins when the composer suddenly decides to cut a concert in London and return home. While on the train, flashbacks reveal his relationship to his wife Anna and her sister Josefina. Both women gave him inspiration, yet Dvorak is clearly troubled in some way as musical excerpts come and go in his creative mind.","genre_ids":[18,36],"popularity":0.1444,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/eqleGeL0HsiJL8hRhmZaIxQlpxc.jpg","release_date":"1980-02-15","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/sXzOqZttAJT4MGtkxZa84zvdgDY.jpg","original_title":"Koncert na konci léta","original_language":"cs"},{"id":763631,"adult":false,"title":"Scars","video":false,"overview":"\"Scars,\" is a short film that explores the horror of domestic abuse. The story follows James through a nightmarish experience of his past relationship with his girlfriend, Camila. He's unconsciously guided around his house by a mysterious presence that forces him to observe his cruel treatment towards her.","genre_ids":[27,53,18,878],"popularity":0.1426,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/aHRNmhVeV0zw3T3a7DLobS8waJn.jpg","release_date":"2019-05-12","vote_average":10,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Scars","original_language":"en"},{"id":1292267,"adult":false,"title":"House Hardy Halloween","video":false,"overview":"A Halloween celebration at the Hardy family compound featuring their wrestling friends the Hurricane, the Boogeyman, the Godfather, and Papa Shango.","genre_ids":[28,35,14,27],"popularity":0.1349,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/dEAlJRxq09Q8e6jQOishBHocTMY.jpg","release_date":"2018-10-28","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/6AO9qHG10QwxCP5vFVp0VAWsGT4.jpg","original_title":"House Hardy Halloween","original_language":"en"},{"id":247309,"adult":false,"title":"Absolutely Fabulous: The Last Shout","video":true,"overview":"Eddy and Patsy prepare to go on a skiing holiday to hopefully indulge in the jet-setting lifestyle of the international celebrity elite when Saffy is proposed to by her stuffy, upper-class boyfriend, Paolo. Eddy hits the slopes and has a near death experience where God appears to her and tells her it's not yet her time. When Eddy comes to, she waits for a sign that she should get involved in Saffy's wedding. As she returns to the house, it appears all hell has broken loose- relatives piling up, practically squatting, and Saffy about to lose her mind. Eddy calms her by throwing money at her as they bond together, planning Saffy's dream wedding. What could go wrong?","genre_ids":[35],"popularity":1.5561,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/2wu5WJat2v071imSGWPdTnBekX0.jpg","release_date":"1996-11-06","vote_average":7.3,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Absolutely Fabulous: The Last Shout","original_language":"en"},{"id":247430,"adult":false,"title":"Meera","video":false,"overview":"Meera, a devotee of Lord Krishna, believes she is married to the lord and rejects her marriage to a Rajput prince. However, her spirituality leads her to face many hardships.","genre_ids":[18,36],"popularity":0.1743,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/fLNGltURx1dFtIzyg55tIx3J5GR.jpg","release_date":"1979-05-18","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/aMj0ka2IlRGiq426MUfrM6jbnME.jpg","original_title":"मीरा","original_language":"hi"},{"id":247472,"adult":false,"title":"Saare Jahaan Se Mehnga","video":false,"overview":"A satire on inflation-hit middle-class Indian family from a small city in North India. The story revolves around our protagonist who is struggling to survive in this spiraling inflation and how he comes up with a solution to battle it, only to find himself in an even bigger mess due to their innocence and naivety.","genre_ids":[35,18],"popularity":0.1231,"vote_count":8,"poster_path":"/gEqSOypPdbcpNkY3S7I17XKGWCc.jpg","release_date":"2013-03-08","vote_average":7.2,"backdrop_path":"/zGnt4Xzubekrpd4rZ8NVMhjWCQ9.jpg","original_title":"Saare Jahaan Se Mehnga","original_language":"hi"},{"id":1472422,"adult":false,"title":"Stardom All Star Grand Queendom 2025","video":true,"overview":"Stardom All Star Grand Queendom 2025 was a professional wrestling event promoted by World Wonder Ring Stardom that took place on April 27, 2025, at Yokohama Arena in Yokohama, Kanagawa, Japan, and was headlined by Saya Kamitani (c) vs. Tam Nakano in a Career vs. Career match for the World of Stardom Championship.","genre_ids":[28,18],"popularity":0.1266,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/qAZeqAxIQ2DjPXlzm2t0yMRRrl1.jpg","release_date":"2025-04-27","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/4KqULOfVdL6JZlGK5CDWV9cpoK4.jpg","original_title":"『カードファイト!! ヴァンガード Divinez presents ALL STAR GRAND QUEENDOM 2025』","original_language":"ja"},{"id":661,"adult":false,"title":"The Marriage of Maria Braun","video":false,"overview":"Maria marries a young soldier in the last days of World War II, only for him to go missing in the war. She must rely on her beauty and ambition to navigate the difficult post-war years alone.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.6702,"vote_count":293,"poster_path":"/tXjZEzlf4WQwZ4Dt53gXeJVuO7p.jpg","release_date":"1979-03-23","vote_average":7.353,"backdrop_path":"/ejp6CZQ64mEvewfit2fSIpOYxGR.jpg","original_title":"Die Ehe der Maria Braun","original_language":"de"},{"id":670,"adult":false,"title":"Oldboy","video":false,"overview":"With no clue how he came to be imprisoned, drugged and tortured for 15 years, a desperate man seeks revenge on his captors.","genre_ids":[18,53,9648,28],"popularity":13.138,"vote_count":9582,"poster_path":"/pWDtjs568ZfOTMbURQBYuT4Qxka.jpg","release_date":"2003-11-21","vote_average":8.241,"backdrop_path":"/sdwjQEM869JFwMytTmvr6ggvaUl.jpg","original_title":"올드보이","original_language":"ko"},{"id":693,"adult":false,"title":"Meet the Fockers","video":false,"overview":"Hard-to-crack ex-CIA man Jack Byrnes and his wife Dina head for the warmer climes of Florida to meet the parents of their son-in-law-to-be, Greg Focker. Unlike their happily matched offspring, the future in-laws find themselves in a situation of opposites that definitely do not attract.","genre_ids":[35,10749],"popularity":4.0227,"vote_count":5062,"poster_path":"/59fXm6N2x7QSbvt6BaBxTNBXGL8.jpg","release_date":"2004-12-22","vote_average":6.255,"backdrop_path":"/porZOny3iVvs5LK0osW1b52wWik.jpg","original_title":"Meet the Fockers","original_language":"en"},{"id":703,"adult":false,"title":"Annie Hall","video":false,"overview":"New York comedian Alvy Singer falls in love with the ditsy Annie Hall.","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"popularity":3.6334,"vote_count":4163,"poster_path":"/dEtjPywhDbAXYjoFfhBC4U9unU7.jpg","release_date":"1977-04-19","vote_average":7.733,"backdrop_path":"/8n9dYsTbXTykzm2Nuy7R2ftapXQ.jpg","original_title":"Annie Hall","original_language":"en"},{"id":742,"adult":false,"title":"Together","video":false,"overvi